This document describes coding standards that are being used in this
project. It's based on LLVM Coding Standards[1].

== Commenting
Comments are one critical part of readability and
maintainability. Everyone knows they should comment, so should
you. When writing comments, write them as English prose, which means
they should use proper capitalization, punctuation, etc.

[1] http://llvm.org/docs/CodingStandards.html
